  "instructions": [
    "Preheat broiler to medium-high heat.",
    "Season the corned beef with salt, pepper, and red pepper flakes.",
    "Heat olive oil in a hot pot vessel over medium-high heat.",
    "Sear the corned beef for 2-3 minutes on each side, or until browned.",
    "Transfer the corned beef to a plate and let rest for 2 minutes.",
    "Meanwhile, toast the pita bread slices under the broiler until lightly browned.",
    "Assemble the broil by slicing the corned beef against the grain and placing it on top of the toasted pita bread.",
    "Drizzle with lemon juice and top with chopped oregano, sliced tomato, and crumbled feta cheese.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
